Homelab Shutdown Program Plan

Program will be made for a Raspberry Pi.

It will be written in python.

It will need to be able to perform these fuctions:
	Run commands at root level on local machine
	Read *.csv files and use values held within
	Run commands on remote machines using ssh
	Perform user verification if program is run manually

Features:
	1. Print information to a physical screen
	2. Require a user to input a pin on a physical keypad to perform shutdown
	3. Use a *.csv file to store remote machine details. (IP, remote User, Command)
	4. Use an aditional *.csv file to run commands on the local raspberry pi
